oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Gallaher home
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Old Roy Gallaher home (log, covered with weather boarding). Col. Joseph Hardin lived here. House burned in 1936. Near corner of Hardin Valley and Campbell Station.
